summary: Adds two spells with lines from Revenge of the Sith
descriptionHtml:
Adds a new lightning storm spell that changes the charge up sound to this http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e_DqV1xdf-Y

And adds a power that lets your character say this
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JD5wWA75skc

Will also play Vader's Noooooo whenever you die
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WWaLxFIVX1s

The spell tomes are at the Riverwood Blacksmith in a barrel.

Pretty simple but I thought it was funny.
author: The Operaters
